      "content": "hey i keep getting a MemoryError when i try to run this script that loads up a bunch of csv files with pandas. i think it might be because i'm using list comprehensions to process the rows instead of generators but im not 100% sure about the difference in how they handle memory. can u explain why a generator would be better here?",
